ygData.messageBody:
not sure of the level range....i'd say anywhere from 27-34 maybe...i know some
things still conned blue to me at 34......and it's in lavastorm....follow the
right wall from the nek zone, go past the big wooden doors <that's najena> and
keep going....when you get to a HUGE pool of lava, there'll be 3 ledges on the
enterior of the crater....the highest one on the left is sol a, the lowest on the
left is sol b, and the one on the right is the temple of sol ro...hope that helps
ya out (:
